```plantuml
@startuml caraml-dev_turing

actor User
participant "Python SDK" as SDK
participant "API Server" as API
participant "Router Engine" as Router
participant "Experiment Engine" as Experiment
participant "Batch Ensembler" as Batch
participant "Kubernetes" as K8s

User -> SDK: Create/Update Router
SDK -> API: POST/PUT /routers
API -> Router: Deploy Router
Router -> Experiment: Register Experiment
Experiment --> Router: Confirmation
Router -> K8s: Deploy Resources
K8s --> Router: Deployment Status
Router --> API: Router Status
API --> SDK: Response
SDK --> User: Router Created/Updated

User -> SDK: Submit Batch Job
SDK -> API: POST /batch-jobs
API -> Batch: Process Job Request
Batch -> K8s: Submit Spark Job
K8s --> Batch: Job Status
Batch --> API: Job Status
API --> SDK: Response
SDK --> User: Job Submitted

User -> SDK: Get Experiment Results
SDK -> API: GET /experiments/{id}/results
API -> Experiment: Retrieve Results
Experiment -> "Logging Backend": Query Results
"Logging Backend" --> Experiment: Results Data
Experiment --> API: Results Response
API --> SDK: Formatted Results
SDK --> User: Display Results

@enduml
```